commit_message:
Update README.md

Clarification of input files (binarisation).

Chromatinsight v3.1

Removing old, unused, project-specific features (PAR regions, Xist, etc).
Using asterisk to identify any chromosome within files.

v3.0

Now using a grouping file rather than basing the analysis on the filename.

v2.3

Fixed bug where the label wasn't being properly taken from the filename because the path of the file was added to the filename string.

v2.2

Added option to not test interTAD regions with interRegionTested parameter in testPrediction.

v 2.1

Fixed bug happening when the genomic region has zero length.
Generating output folder if it doesn't exist
